name: SERIE 3  AVIGNON 50ml
campo_tres: Powerful and intense, Avignon evokes the medieval city in the south of France which surpassed Rome as the Catholic Church's power center in the 14th century. It's the scent of gothic cathedrals and Papal palaces, of tapestries imbued with centuries of incense. Of cold marble steps, holy relics and dark confessions. The recognizable smells of frankincense and myrrh open the high mass of Avignon, giving way to the almost eye-smarting, gloriously smoky and resinous heart. A dry vanilla and soft Roman chamomile dull the edges of this reverent fragrance. Beautiful, dark and mysterious, Avignon takes its place among the most talked about and admired of CdG's entire line.

name: SERIE 3 KYOTO 50ml
campo_tres: Kyoto is a spiritual journey to the serene temples of the city known as Heart of Japan. Dry and calm, the cedar note in Kyoto is evident, swirling with the earthy scents of spicy, smoky vetiver and the juniper-meets-evergreen aroma of cypress. Serene and earthbound, Kyoto's quiet power is never harsh. it's a meditative scent, bringing to mind relaxing in one of Kyoto's legendary rotenburo (outdoor hot spring baths) nestled among the legendary cypress trees.

campo_seis: Comme des Garçons 2 plays with complements and contrasts... with reflection and opacity... with mirrors and brilliance... with light and shadow... with earth and the energy of the sun. name: DSQUARED SHE WOOD EDP 50ML
campo_tres: El primer perfume femenino de Dsquared2 es She Wood, una fragancia amaderada floral que exalta la sensualidad y elegancia de la mujer que la lleva a través de la madera, principal inspiración de She Wood. En su salida destacan las notas de limón, pétalos de jazmín y neroli bigarade en el corazón, la flor y las hojas de la violeta, heliotropo y almizcle, en el fondo, madera de cedro, vetiver y ámbar vegetal
campo_seis: Dsquared2 ’s first women’s perfume has a sensual, brilliant character. The Caten twins nurture a true sentiment and deep love for their homeland of Canada. The first ever women’s scent is called SHE WOOD. Dean and Dan dedicate their perfume to women whom are sensual, with subtle elegance. Directed toward a woman that is vibrant and vivacious, delicate, nature loving, at times quite distant, and someone who loves to cast her own light, dreaming of losing herself there as she seeks freedom and new emotions. The concept of SHE WOOD is pink light, giving a refined textured feel. SHE WOOD is to evoke sensuality and passion, nature, freedom, and life. The bottle of SHE WOOD is made from the soft wood of the North American Walnut tree, enclosed within the square shaped bottle is a splendid pink gleam which exalts it and endows it with womanly sensuality.

name: C.CHRISTIAN X FOR MEN 50ml
campo_tres: Poco convencional, exótico y dominante: los afrodisíacos naturales más poderosos conocidos por la humanidad. X for Men. El carácter imponente de X puede atribuirse al orris, la raíz del lirio, estimada en la antigüedad por su poder y majestuosidad
campo_seis: Unconventional, exotic and harnessing the most powerful natural aphrodisiacs known to mankind. X for Men. The commanding character of X can be attributed to Orris, root of the Iris flower, prized in ancient times for its power and majesty

name: C.CHRISTIAN 1872 WOMEN 50ml
campo_tres: Perfumes tradicionales cuyos nombres homenajean el año en el que la Reina Victoria otorgó su corona a la perfumería. 1872 for Women.170 rosas son necesarias para crear una sola gota de la preciada Rose de Mai, asociada con la pureza y la presencia de un ángel.

name: LUBIN GIN FIZZ 100ml
campo_tres: GIN FIZZ  con una nota hesperiada verde al comienzo, es la elegancia muy parisina del iris, enriquecido por un ramillete floral de jazmín y rosa que se posa enseguida sobre una base de maderas especiadas. Un perfume que marcará este decenio. Muy Chic, fresco y chispeante. Su nombre evoca el cóctel en boga en los 'bares americanos' de París de aquel año
campo_seis: 'A fresh and flowery chypre with lemony top notes over an aldehyde and musky base.' Gin Fizz by the house of Lubin has been on the market since July 2009 -actualized by Thomas Fontaine-. In 1955, one movie star captivated the crowds. To the entire world she was the embodiment of American elegance and her mysterious charm even captured the heart of a Prince. To honor of her extraordinary beauty, Lubin created a perfume which marked the decade- An extremely chic fragrance, sparkling and fresh, evoking that year’s most fashionable cocktail, Gin Fizz.The fragrance was first created in 1955 by celebrated perfumer Henri Giboulet as a tribute to Grace Kelly in the year she won an Oscar for her role in The Country Girl. The name is inspired by a cocktail that was in fashion at the time in the American bars of Paris, and was synonymous with joie de vivre and a fashionably festive lifestyle.

name: BENDELIRIOUS EDP 50ML
campo_tres: Bendelirious. Este aroma único y ligeramente atrevido, creado por Antoine Lie de Givaudan Paris, se inspira en lo que podriamos llamar la Chica Bendel, confidente pero juguetona, cuyos instintos invaden cada momento de su vida. De apariencia bella, interesante y noble, de forma natural, es atractiva, culta y femenina, un espíritu libre. Coleccionista de lo auténtico y maravilloso, reúne piezas excéntricas, xpresivas opulentas tanto vintage como contemporáneas, consiguiendo mezclarlas de forma natural. Simplemente hace lo que quiere, va donde quiere y compra lo que quiere.
campo_seis: Fresh Soft Floral suitable for females, with notes of grapefruit essence, champagne accord, cherry lollipop accord, violette leaves absolute, orris absolute, orris butter, leather, accord, vetiver accord, musk, and tonka beans absolute.

name: EDP ROSSY DE PALMA 50ML
campo_uno: EAU DE PROTECTION ROSSY DE PALMA
campo_tres: Rossy de Palma fue creada por dos narices extraordinarias (Antoine Maisondieu y Antoine Lie de Givaudan). Animados por el fuego de esta mujer, las narices han incorporado esta fantástica visión. Han creado un perfume de protección para ella, un refugio en el campo de batalla del amor. Defensivo y transparente, Rossy oculta y revela. Para ella, una caricia es necesaria, cuando los que se encuentran a su alrededor se encuentran noqueados. Los perfumistas han extraído lo más profundo de ella, su esencia. Han destilado su dulzura y exprimido el jugo de su corazón.
campo_seis: A Classical Floral, spicy rose perfume, with notes of ginger, black pepper from Madagascar, bergamot, rose of Bulgaria, jasmine, benzoin, patchouli, incense, and cocoa.

campo_tres: La fantasía absoluta, mujer que desarma a los hombres con su sofisticada seducción. Empolvado floral afrutado con base de cuero amaderado, evoca la femme fatale que toda mujer lleva dentro.

name: RIEN EDP 50ML
campo_tres: La meticulosa elegancia y la hipnótica belleza de Dorian Gray, inspiran este perfume donde la nada lo es todo. Bajo una apariencia suave como el mohair o el cachemire, se desvela un perfume animal con intensas notas de cuero.
campo_seis: A Classical unisex, Dry Woods perfume with notes of incense, rose, leather, cistus, oakmoss, patchouli, amber, cumin, black pepper, and ahyde.

name: VIERGES ET TOREROS EDP 50ML
campo_tres: El sol inunda la arena, el orgullo de los hombres se impone. Mezclado con las notas animales, destaca una de las flores más olorosas- el nardo, masculina por tradición, esta flor se suaviza, acercando así a la Virgen y al Torero.
campo_seis: A Crisp Woods perfume suitable for men, with notes of bergamot, nutmeg, pepper, cardamom, ylang ylang, tuberose, leather, animalis, costus, patchouli, and vetiver.

name: SKARB EDT NATURAL SPRAY 100ml
campo_tres: La fragancia de la melancolía. Con levística, ajenjo, manzanilla romana, extracto de cebada, incienso, mirra y almizcle.
campo_seis: Skarb means treasure in polish and its the name of the first perfume by Humiecki  Graef. No other than the famous perfumer Christophe Laudamiel himself, prize winning 'enfant terrible' of the perfume industry, created this extraordinary scent. Humiecki and Graef asked Laudamiel to create a perfume that captures the state of 'how men cry' - eruptive and sensual. Pictures from Slavic culture, as well as how they deal with melancholia and happiness served as inspiration. The result is a perfume that combines raw eruption, sensual strength, melancholic warmth and deep mysticism. The form of the composition departs from convention as the scent is not constructed pyramidally as is traditional, but star-shaped. In contrast to the rigid categories of head, heart and base notes, the star-shape allows the scent to reflect deep emotions and the individual ingredients can be perceived. In the centre of the star is the core of the emotions: the feeling of shed tears. The different points of the star represent the facets of the concept: the watery and purifying effect, a deep slavic soul, childhood memories, as well as the soft and animalistic feeling of naked skin. The scents of absinth, myrrh, patchouly, sandal wood .... reflect in succession the melancholia upon with the perfumer based his creation.

name: GESTE EDT NATURAL SPRAY 100ml
campo_tres: La fragancia de la intensidad, con ámbar, almizcle, resina de pino silvestre y violetas
campo_seis: Powdered violets and a brisk musk that puts one in mind of freshly starched hotel sheets lead off this intriguing, elusive fragrance. Spritz it on and then go about your business, because it takes a few moments for this to come into its own. Geste is about the intensity of quiet things. The violets lose their powdery quality and become clear and sweetly melancholy, nestling into a comfy bed of amber-laced musk. Some musks are clean and some are dirty, and this seems to dance on the edge right between the two -- innocent and seductive by turns. Soft fir resin adds an appealing, distinctly modern edge. The resin has a hint of the therapeutic about it, like bath salts or a spa sauna, and adds a comforting roughness that counters the delicacy of the violets. Those contradictions – dirty and clean, rough and gentle – are what make this fragrance so fascinating. They also explain why this works so well on both men and women. Discreetly risqué, this has the genteel recklessness of an afternoon tryst in a luxury suite. Subtle and unique.

name: ASKEW EDT NATURAL SPRAY 100ML
campo_tres: La fragancia de la furia, contiene notas de Vetiver, alquitrán de corteza de abedul, cardamono de Guatemala, cuero suave, jengibre, mimosa egipcia y pomelo.
campo_seis: Inspired by fury. There is a bold swagger to the sharp, almost medicinal opening that puts one instantly on notice- stinging grapefruit, percolating ginger and the bite of something mentholated. As the fragrance develops, smoother elements such as soft leather and earthy vetiver come into play – but they never coax Askew into being comforting or tame. There is a crackling of static electricity like the air before a thunderstorm and the dark and brooding shadow of birch tar, which dominates the blend. A sharp and sweet gingered mimosa fizzes on the surface like the rakish grin of a con man. Dynamic and volatile, this is a classic men’s scent deconstructed by bad boy perfumer Christophe Laudamiel. He takes all the traditional elements – citrus, spice, leather – and tweaks them to create a fiercely compelling fragrance with an angular beauty all its own

name: MULTIPLE ROUGE NATURAL SPRAY 100ml
campo_tres: La fragancia de la locura. Notas de frutas rojas silvestres, naranja congelada, hueso de melocotón, piña verde, cilantro vietnamita, violeta verde y immortelle absolute.
campo_seis: Fresh and fruity taken to a strange and wonderful new level. Imagine a botanical Willy Wonka, creating the ultimate fruit in a hydroponic frenzy- a luscious melonberry, with hints of peach and pineapple thrown in for good measure and a dose of acidic tartness to keep it lively. The magical mystery fruit tantalizes -- one moment it seems completely familiar, you’re certain you know what it is, then it morphs into something exotic and unrecognizable. Cool, airy ozonic notes ruffle up against warm, velvety immortelle and occasional wafts of dry cinnamon and piquant cilantro float by. It is the Garden of Eden on a faraway planet – lush and delicious and a little bit alien. There is something gleeful about this fragrance – it has the breathless giddiness of seeing the dawn come up after an all-night rave. The dry down has a trippy, lighter-than air freshness that is tethered by a persistent murmur of warm, sweet earthiness – and that combination is what makes this so compulsively wearable. A fragrance to take you to your happy place.

name: CLEMENCY NATURAL SPRAY 100ml
campo_tres: La fragancia del orgullo. Con rosa, tilo, cassie absolute, madera, cuero, leche
campo_seis: Motherhood exalted in that most special of ways…by adoring sons. The reality of the giving nature of most mothers is little mud, some soup stains, crusty Play-Doh and maybe some yogurty lip blobs on the windows. Clemency takes a loftier path, looking to capture a mother as a figure of serene knowingness, a regal and proud figure amidst the chaos of nurturing a life. Rose is clear and familiar at the opening- the contrast of the sweet notes of acacia and linden against rich leather are harmonious rather than clashing. Woven throughout is the softness of a barely-there milk note. A grand perfume that spotlights the many faces of this woman-on-a-pedestal, from tender, generous, glowing and forgiving to proud, serious, stern and inscrutable, Clemency is a beautifully rendered take on a pivotal figure- the mother.

name: C.CHRISTIAN 1872 MEN 50ml
campo_tres: Perfumes tradicionales cuyos nombres homenajean el año en el que la Reina Victoria otorgó su corona a la perfumería. 1872 for Men. Petit grain clásico, mandarina y lavanda se combinan con la hierba sagrada del Imperio Romano y con salvia sclarea para conferir energía y vigor
campo_seis: Traditional perfumes named as a tribute to the year Queen Victoria granted her crown to the House. 1872 for Men. Classic petit grain, mandarin and lavender combine with the Roman Empire's sacred herb Clary Sage to bestow energy and invigoration

name: C.CHRISTIAN X WOMEN 50ml
campo_tres: Poco convencional, exótico y dominante: los afrodisíacos naturales más poderosos conocidos por la humanidad. X for Women. Manifiestamente raro, el jazmín egipcio se recoge en las orillas del Nilo al atardecer y Cleopatra lo usó para conquistar el corazón de Marco Antonio.
campo_seis: Unconventional, exotic and harnessing the most powerful natural aphrodisiacs known to mankind. X for Women. Notoriously rare Egyptian Jasmine is gathered from the banks of the Nile at dusk and was used by Cleopatra to capture Mark Anthony's heart.

name: PERFUME EXOTIC 50ml
campo_tres: There is something edible about Exotic’s blackcurrant dipped in black chocolate notes – the chocolate effect rises from the patchouli-vanilla accord – but this is far from a gourmand scent. Patchouli plunges into an earthy base of vetiver, laced with the animalic aromas of black truffle and dirty musk. Ylang-ylang suffuses the blend with a tropical languor. Thick and lush as the jungle beyond the white-sand beach, a little foreboding for all its musky charms, Exotic beckons like a voyage into the heart of darkness.
campo_seis: There is something edible about Exotic’s blackcurrant dipped in black chocolate notes – the chocolate effect rises from the patchouli-vanilla accord – but this is far from a gourmand scent. name: PERFUME SEDUCTIVE 50ml
campo_tres: This deeply carnal blend of animalic musk, soft, broken-in leather and mysterious green maté is one sexy beast of a scent. A bracing beginning, almost mentholated in its briskness, quickly morphs into pure seduction. Yerba maté is a traditional steeped herbal drink of South America – soothing and energizing simultaneously. It is sometimes described as a cross between coffee and tea, but it truly has an intriguing character all its own. In this scent it resembles a more intense green tea, which spikes the citrus of the opening. A cool iris rings out the smoothness of the leather, but nothing can take the growl out of the dark, sensuous musk at the heart of this fragrance. Dangerous and powerful.

name: PERFUME PURÉ 50ml
campo_tres: The initial simplicity of Pure is deceptive, as it opens with what seems to be a straightforward blend of juicy tropical fruits. As the fragrance develops, however, other parts of the composition come to the fore, until gradually a heart of luminous sugar dusted white jasmine and rose appears, singing above a glass-smooth base of amber, sandalwood and soft oakmoss. Pure is an innocent fragrance with a twist- a masterfully blended perfume for all seasons.

name: PERFUME ADVENTURESS 50ml
campo_tres: Take the most luscious, juicy, so-ripe-it’s-about-ready-to-fall-off-the-tree peach and blend it with the warmest, creamiest sandalwood to create an intoxicating concoction that is decadently voluptuous. Delightfully tart citrus eases our way into a satisfyingly sweet peach so vivid that you can almost feel the fuzzy skin. Velvety and warm and languid – the peach, sandalwood and soft musk nuzzle into each other in the most sultry manner. We can’t quite picture getting up out of our chaise lounge with this on, but it is so drop dead glamorous that we assume it will bring the adventure to us. Sensuous and glowing, this makes us purr.

name: PERFUME DELICATE 50ml
campo_tres: Imagine walking into an English garden, just after a rain. The clouds have broken, and sun warms the rolling lawn and deep borders of spring flowers. You reach into a patch of lilies of the valley, its flowers not quite open, and crush a stem in your fingers to smell the green, yet sweet, scent. All around you stirs a breeze of luscious bluebells, hyacinths, and roses. You know that days like these are rare and end all too quickly. This is the fragrance of Delicate, one of Boadicea the Victorious's most popular offerings. A steady pulse of galbanum courses through Delicate's bouquet of spicy spring flowers, keeping the scent fresh and never cloying, despite its lush composition. A whisper of clean musk adds to the feeling of a morning in the garden. But don't let its name fool you- Delicate has definite presence. This is the scent of laughing friends on April mornings, of wood nymphs, of long-awaited love letters.

name: PERFUME ALLURING 50ml
campo_tres: A rose in full bloom on a bright summer morning – what could be more beautiful? We don’t know precisely what summer fruits are involved, but to us it smells like berries – sweet, ripe and luscious with a little burst of tartness. There is a delicate and enchanting ylang ylang with a tiny hint of soapiness. And there, at the heart, is a perfect dewy rose, proudly unfurling its glorious petals under the brilliant June sky. This is a rose that is both lush and straightforward. Its unfussy warm simplicity keeps it youthful and fresh. The subtle base notes add a sun-drenched feel and the fruity grace notes evoke the lushness of a summer garden, but never overshadow the lovely evocation of the queen of flowers. Graceful and, as the name promises, completely alluring.

Graceful and, as the name promises, completely alluring.

name: PERFUME ALLURING 50ml
campo_tres: A rose in full bloom on a bright summer morning – what could be more beautiful? We don’t know precisely what summer fruits are involved, but to us it smells like berries – sweet, ripe and luscious with a little burst of tartness. There is a delicate and enchanting ylang ylang with a tiny hint of soapiness. And there, at the heart, is a perfect dewy rose, proudly unfurling its glorious petals under the brilliant June sky. Graceful and, as the name promises, completely alluring.

name: PERFUME ASMAR OUD 60ml
campo_tres: Dusky scent, of earth and sun, of tanned skin and warm sand. A concentrated but pleasant amber fragrance, strong and delicate thanks to the careful blend of warm notes. A foray into the dreamy heart of a thousand and one nights. When Dorian Grey meets Scheherazade. With bergamot, honey, carnation, coffee, amber cigar, grape marc, amber, tobacoo, chamois, musk and vanilla.

name: PERFUME BURQA OUD 60ml
campo_tres: Like pure blood flowing, mystical and fluid, from every temple, with tones of Chinese ink and bewitched by essences of hard wood, this anthracite fragrance is a liquid incense with a notable prestige and elegance. With notes of jasmine, rose, black violet, cardamom, sage, leather, benzoin, myrrh, black ink, rubber sap, black amber, teck wood, patchouli and guaiac wood

name: PERFUME FAM OUD 60ml
campo_tres: An intense vibration of flamboyant red spices combine in perfect harmony with the warm woodland tones, in an embrace of powdery floral notes. Created by the genius of the Mughal emperors, this sophisticated fragrance exudes all the charm of Agar wood, associated with acanthus. Featuring saffron, chili, fresh rose, oud, cashmeran, rose powder, rubber sap, vinyl accord, sandalwood, cedar, milk and red musk.

campo_tres: This perfume, black as coal, hard, tactile, with opaque luminous facets, is stratified with agarwood. Essences of nagarmotha, natural sandalwood and white roses make Kanz the perfume of Maharajas With jasmine, rose, nagarmotha, oud and sandalwood.

name: NEKTAR HAJJ 30ML
campo_tres: Created around noble notes, the appeal of Hajj reveals sweet fresh spices, such as star anise or ginger, associated with a stimulating background of warm notes. This fragrance with its original scent transmits all the richness of oriental perfumes. Enclosed by hints of various woods and succulent citrus, this balanced line gives the perfume a fragrance which evokes wisdom and spirituality. The notes include bergamot, mandarin, star anise, rosewood, osmanthus, licorice, ginger, patchouli, tolu balsam, tobacco and vetiver.

name: BIJOU ROMANTIQUE 50ML
campo_tres: Este es el retrato de una dama. Ella puede ser vista en el cameo femenino, en el perfil suave, delicada, en la imagen de ensueño de una belleza incandescente. Lo que antes era cubierta ha sido  tallada en relieve por un artesano dedicado, a emerger como una mujer idealizada. Joyas, también ... "desarrollado por el perfumista Mathilde Bijaoui, con notas de bergamota, limón, pimienta rosa, ylang-ylang, salvia, iris, coco, vetiver, benjuí y vainilla.
campo_seis: This is the portrait of a lady. She can be seen in the feminine cameo, in the soft, delicate profile, in the dreamy image of an incandescent beauty. What once was shell has been carved in relief by a devoted artisan, to emerge as an idealized woman. Jewels, too…” Developed by perfumer Mathilde Bijaoui, with notes of bergamot, lemon, pink pepper, ylang-ylang, sage, iris, coconut, vetiver, benzoin and vanilla.
